    94тЖТ// Equals compares Constraints with other Constraints
    95тЖТ// for equality. This may not represent logical equivalence
    96тЖТ// of compared constraints.
    97тЖТ// e.g. even though '>0.1,>0.2' is logically equivalent
    98тЖТ// to '>0.2' it is *NOT* treated as equal.
    99тЖТ//
   100тЖТ// Missing operator is treated as equal to '=', whitespaces
   101тЖТ// are ignored and constraints are sorted before comparison.
   102тЖТfunc (cs Constraints) Equals(c Constraints) bool {
   103тЖТ	if len(cs) != len(c) {
   104тЖТ		return false
